videos.description: Auburn strikes first as Jarrett Stidham finds a wide-open JaTarvious Whitlow for a 66-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Auburn's Stidham connects with Whitlow for 66-yard TD

videos.description: JaTarvious Whitlow is dominating early as he powers through the line for a 2-yard Auburn touchdown, his second of the game.
videos.headline: Auburn's Whitlow powers in 2nd TD of game

videos.description: Auburn is pulling away early as JaTarvious Whitlow goes untouched for a 1-yard touchdown, his third of the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: Whitlow walks in 3rd TD of the 1st quarter

videos.description: Rondale Moore takes the ball on a jet sweep and scores a 7-yard Purdue touchdown.
videos.headline: Purdue's Moore gets to the edge for 7-yard TD

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham shows off his arm strength as he finds Darius Slayton for a 74-yard Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Stidham throws a dime to Slayton for 74-yard TD

videos.description: Auburn's Darius Slayton turns on the jets as he blows past the Purdue defense for a 52-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Slayton shows off SEC speed as he escapes for 52-yard TD

videos.description: Purdue's David Blough's pass gets tipped up in the air and is snagged by Big Kat Bryant who takes it 20 yards for an Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Big Kat Bryant pounces on INT for TD

videos.description: Tensions are running high as Purdue and Auburn get into a scuffle right before the half.
videos.headline: Scuffle breaks out between Auburn and Purdue

videos.description: Auburn breaks its all time bowl game record for points in a half as Jarrett Stidham finds Darius Slayton for a 34-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Slayton's 34-yd TD sets Auburn's bowl game record for 1st-half points

videos.description: Auburn breaks Alabama's 65-year record for most points in a bowl game by a SEC team on Jarrett Stidham's 5-yard touchdown toss to Ryan Davis.
videos.headline: Auburn sets SEC record for most points in bowl game
